                    <td>
                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">NOTICE</center>
                        
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">TRADE DESCRIPTIONS
                            (PROVISION OF INFORMATION ON NATURAL FEI CUI) ORDER</center>
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">(<ref href="/hk/cap362M">Chapter 362 subsidiary<br></br>legislation
                            M</ref>)</center>
                        
                    </td>
                    
                    <td></td>
                    
                    <td>
                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">告示</center>
                        
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">《商品說明(提供關於天然翡翠的資料)令》</center>
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">(<ref href="/hk/cap362M">第362章，附屬法例M</ref>)</center>
                        
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                    </td>
                    
                    <td></td>
                    
                    <td>
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p class="first_line_indent_24">Under the laws of Hong Kong—</p>
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                        <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" id="ID_1571106179373_001" name="a" temporalId="sch0_a"><num value="a">(<i>a</i>)</num><content>only jade that falls within the definition in the Trade
                                Descriptions (Definition of Fei Cui and Natural Fei Cui) Regulation
                                    (<ref href="/hk/cap362K">Cap. 362 sub. leg. K</ref>) can be
                                described as “fei cui”;</content></paragraph>
                        <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" id="ID_1571106179373_002" name="b" temporalId="sch0_b"><num value="b">(<i>b</i>)</num><content class="align_justified">fei cui may be described as “natural”
                                only if it has not been subjected to any treatment or process which
                                altered its crystalline structure or original colour.</content></paragraph>
                    </td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td>
                        <p class="first_line_indent_24">根據香港法例——</p>
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                        <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" id="ID_1571106179373_003" name="a" temporalId="sch0_a"><num value="a">(<i>a</i>)</num><content>只有符合《商品說明(翡翠及天然翡翠的定義)規例》(<ref href="/hk/cap362K">第362章，附屬法例K</ref>)中的定義的玉石，方可被稱為“翡翠”；</content></paragraph>
                        <paragraph xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" id="ID_1571106179373_004" name="b" temporalId="sch0_b"><num value="b">(<i>b</i>)</num><content class="align_justified">翡翠必須沒有經過任何改變其晶體結構或原色的處理或工序，方可被稱為“天然”。</content></paragraph>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                    </td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td>
                        <marker xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" role="blank-line"></marker>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        
                        
                        <content xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" class="first_line_indent_24 align_justified">A detailed invoice or
                            receipt shall be issued by the supplier in respect of every article of
                            natural fei cui supplied.</content>
                        
                        
                    </td>
                    
                    <td></td>
                    
                    <td>
                        
                        
                        <content xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" class="first_line_indent_24 align_justified">供應人須就所供應的每件天然翡翠製品發出詳細的發票或收據。</content>
                        
                        
                        
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2008/ln167">L.N. 167 of
            2008</ref>)</sourceNote></text></schedule></main></subLeg>